Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.68,0:00:05.97,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.02,0:00:08.68,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged a vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.81,0:00:13.86,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.90,0:00:18.99,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.45,0:00:31.71,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The future that the forbidden fruit foretells...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:40.17,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change the dream into reality
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:52.06,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The ending that everybody wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.02,0:00:55.31,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:58.07,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged our vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.15,0:01:02.95,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.11,0:01:08.45,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Someday I'll show you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.45,0:01:17.75,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A bright and ideal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.10,0:01:35.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of how she came to\Nher conclusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.31,0:01:37.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she knows the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.65,0:01:40.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she gives this information\Nto the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:44.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll figure out that I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.82,0:01:47.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to finish her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.16,0:01:48.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:52.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:57.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been going over\Nwhat you just told me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:01.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I think that we should investigate\Nthat theory as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.09,0:02:03.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:04.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:06.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you told this to anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.84,0:02:08.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.93,0:02:12.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:14.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But how are you going to\Nrub her out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.18,0:02:16.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be bad\Nif you did it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:19.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already figured that out...\Nwithout you telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.65,0:02:22.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! So out in the open.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:26.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you tell me the date\Nand time of the bus-jacking incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:30.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was on December 20,\Nin front of Asagao Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:33.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At 11:02.\NHeaded to Space Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.58,0:02:40.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,December 20.\NHeaded to Space Land, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:41.96,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz24.559\pos(326,427)}Shoko Maki\N\N\N\N\N\NSuicide\N\N\N\N\N\NJanuary 1, 2007
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:42.55,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz24.559\move(323,427,298,405,17,580)}Shoko Maki\N\N\N\N\N\NSuicide\N\N\N\N\N\NJanuary 1, 2007
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:43.94,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz24.559\move(295,405,184,343,10,1387)}Shoko Maki\N\N\N\N\N\NSuicide\N\N\N\N\N\NJanuary 1, 2007
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:50.40,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz25.494\move(384,368,367,335,5421,5421)}Commits suicide in such a way\Nthat nobody will be inconvenienced\Nand her body will not be discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:50.40,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz25.494\move(422,402,403,369,5421,5421)}Dies by implementing this plan\Nwithin 48 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:53.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now no one will find her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:55.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they do find her,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:02:58.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll assume that she killed herself\Nbecause of her fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:03.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk, what's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:13.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry for questioning\Nall of you individually.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:16.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is not one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:21.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, how can you definitely\Nsay that he's not among us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:27.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I set some traps\Nto check if you were Kira, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.09,0:03:31.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't feel the need to\Nset them off on any of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:35.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:42.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After he told us to\Nturn off our cell phones...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:44.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:45.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just about finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:48.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Enter with your own key.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:51.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:54.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.37,0:03:58.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's all right, I'll report this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.54,0:04:02.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'd like to report it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:06.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After talking to you, I've decided to\Ndo it as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:10.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just ten seconds until 1:15...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:22.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see how this woman dies,\Nbut I can't be caught following her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:28.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...hurry to your death!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:44.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will definitely be caught, won't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:45.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:54.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Time is already up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:04:58.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:01.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't this woman leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:06.90,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,183)\fad(292,459)}Suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:03.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My tests have proved that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:06.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can make people kill themselves\Nby writing "suicide."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:10.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The criminals I tested all hanged\Nthemselves at the times that I specified.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:13.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've proved many times that\NI should be able
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:15.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to control her within\Nthese circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:18.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:25.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:26.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:29.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he was laughing oddly when\NI was writing in the Death Note...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:31.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:34.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The way he laughed when I asked\Nfor her name was also bizarre...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:38.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It occurred when it had\Nto do with her name...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:40.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An alias!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.23,0:05:52.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you all for working so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:55.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This person is Watari?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:57.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, where are your usual clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:06:00.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had dressed as I usually do,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:01.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it would be like telling everyone\NI'm Watari.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:05.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would also give away Ryuzaki's\Nlocation in this hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:07.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:13.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Showing my face in front of you\Nall means you've won Ryuzaki's trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:16.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I feel kind of honored...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:22.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, I've brought what\Nyou've requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:25.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please pass them out to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:26.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:31.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These are everyone's new police IDs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:33.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,New?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:37.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An alias.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:38.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only thing it could be!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:42.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk can see her real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:44.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he was laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:48.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This woman was being careful\Nfrom the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:50.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:54.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She believes that Raye died...\Nbecause he showed his ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:58.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she's acting without\Nrevealing her identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:00.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:02.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's even harder to ask the real name
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:05.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,of someone who has already\Ngiven an alias.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:08.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I keep asking her persistently,\Nshe'll get suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:12.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, it's suspicious\Nthat I knew she was using an alias.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:16.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be getting back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:19.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone might have come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:22.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.\NI suppose you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:25.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopefully someone did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:26.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:31.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.67,0:07:33.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would also be unnatural\Nto try to turn her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:40.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:42.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If my father calls...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:47.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised her that I'd let her\Ntalk to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:49.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over if he calls!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:51.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:57.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What am I thinking about?\NI can just turn off my cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:00.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:04.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to find out her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:08.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her purse, her pocket,\Nshe's got to have a driver's license...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.33,0:08:10.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,or some sort of personal ID\Non her somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:12.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:14.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If things become desperate,\NI can use force...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:16.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:18.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything that'll\Ncause a stir in a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.05,0:08:20.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to get her to\Nsomewhere isolated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:24.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where? What explanation\Ncan I offer her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:27.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's too careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:29.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I've got to change\Nmy plan of attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:30.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:33.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can get her name without\Nsetting any alarms off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:37.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.19,0:08:40.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can always do the eye deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:42.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no different from putting\Non contact lenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:44.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be finished in a few seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:49.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't have my remaining life\Nhalved by the likes of this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:53.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't ever consider the deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:54.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:56.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Shinigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:58.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:08:59.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:02.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still have business\Nat the police department?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:05.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be all right by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:08.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:12.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our names and ranks are all fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:14.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fake police IDs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:18.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira requires a name\Nand a face to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:21.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We are challenging Kira\Nwith that premise in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:23.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:27.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But a police officer with a fake ID is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:30.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, if Kira needs a name to kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:35.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,an alias would go a long way\Nin protecting our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:37.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We should carry these around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:39.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:40.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:44.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you have to give out your\Nname to strangers,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:46.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,use the alias in your IDs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:48.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:52.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful not to take\Nthem out
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:53.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,within the police headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:55.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It could cause problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.56,0:09:57.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:10:03.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...\NI want everyone to wear these belts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:04.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Belts?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.57,0:10:07.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a tracking device\Nin the buckle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:11.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, Ryuzaki will know\Nyour whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:13.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you press the buckle twice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:17.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My cell phone will ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:22.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll call you back immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:26.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the morning, you will go to work\Nat the police department.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:28.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, using this method...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:31.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall confirm our\Nhotel and room number.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:34.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please use this\Nfor emergencies as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:36.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is kind of cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:39.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we're a special force\Nchasing Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:40.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:42.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't child's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:43.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't joke around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.82,0:10:45.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:48.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.74,0:10:52.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I have gained\Nconfidence in my theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.74,0:10:53.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:03.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Ryuk started talking\Nabout the eye bargain...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:05.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake.\NShe's using an alias.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:11.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, with her theory that\NKira was on the bus...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:14.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and given the people Raye Penber\Nwas in charge of investigating,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:16.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the police will immediately suspect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:21.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, she's leaving.\NIs that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:25.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be about five minutes until\Nshe reaches the police headquarters...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Think...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:30.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I get her name\Nwithin five minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:47.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to the police headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:51.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone from the task force\Nhas returned, I'm finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:55.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I've got to find out\Nher real name and finish her off...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:58.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now there are only three minutes\Nuntil she reaches the police headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:01.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.02,0:12:04.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:05.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.65,0:12:06.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:09.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I haven't told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.24,0:12:11.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:16.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to contact anyone\Ndirectly in headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:17.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:19.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to conduct this conversation\Nnaturally and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:22.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,connect it to something\Nthat she'll latch onto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:25.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Within that time, I'll draw out her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:27.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:29.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:32.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that it's odd\Nthat there's no one at headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:34.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.43,0:12:36.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was strange, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:42.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The team investigating Kira is structured\Nso no one knows who is involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:48.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the public knows how\Nthe team is structured,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:52.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,a tragedy like the one involving\Nyour fiancé may happen again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.41,0:12:59.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:03.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you were told\Nthat no one was at the headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:06.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:10.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you will never be allowed to talk\Ndirectly to someone from headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:16.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty clever.\NAs expected of you, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:20.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you know so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:23.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's pretty sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:27.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:29.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:32.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I'm a detective\Nfrom the task force.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:36.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a detective from the task force?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.91,0:13:37.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:41.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L is currently in charge of the task force.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:42.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:43.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:48.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L was troubled because there\Nweren't enough detectives at headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:51.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Many quit because they're afraid of Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:54.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a high school student, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:58.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have helped the police\Nsolve two cases in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.68,0:14:01.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So he was sold by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:04.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can enter the headquarters\Nwhenever I wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:07.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm allowed to investigate\Non my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:11.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the people who\Nare currently at headquarters...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:15.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,are the chosen few who...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:19.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,can be trusted and whose\Nabilities are reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:32.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.96,0:14:36.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But just in case,\NI think I'll visit the headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:38.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:42.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:46.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just told you that\Nyou can't talk to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:49.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to talk directly to L.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:58.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\Nwho's at headquarters now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:15:00.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:01.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.37,0:15:05.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have at least one person\Nthere at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:06.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.58,0:15:08.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa, if you could stay there for today...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:09.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:11.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can get there quickly from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Maki, please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.63,0:15:16.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to meet L.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.76,0:15:17.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:25.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He might...allow me to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:29.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I only followed his orders from\Nbeyond a computer screen, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:36.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Two years ago in America\NI worked on a case under L.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:38.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You worked under L?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:44.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Until three months ago,\NI was an FBI agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:48.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it...\NI can use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:51.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:56.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no wonder. Your actions are\Nnot those of an amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.88,0:16:00.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You move carefully and wisely\Nas you get to the heart of the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.97,0:16:02.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to learn from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.43,0:16:06.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing how you can\Nline up all those lies like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:10.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I must approach this case\Nin my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.23,0:16:14.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to suspect the police\Nand even the people within task force.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:17.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I trust L.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:21.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that if I went to headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:27.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and have them verify my name and face...\NI'd be able to speak directly to L.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:28.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:33.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did you tell me that\Nyou wanted to talk to L?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:36.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I wasn't allowed to see\Nsomeone from the task force,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:39.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was angry and then\NI ran into someone
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:41.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who claimed to be\Nthe son of the lead detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:44.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:47.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:50.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You seemed like L.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt that you two are similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:04.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we investigate the\Ncase together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:05.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:10.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you work as\Nan agent in the task force?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:13.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, not just anybody is allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:17.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we need people like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:21.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You could be doing more than\Ngathering general information.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:24.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were an FBI agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:27.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're more talented than\Nour current detectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:29.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even L trusted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:34.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To join the task force,\Nyou need proper identification,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.69,0:17:37.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,a recommendation from\Na current detective on the team,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:39.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and finally L's permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:41.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to join\Nthe task force?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:45.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be fate to meet you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:47.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll recommend you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:53.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:55.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just became a little excited...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:57.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:18:01.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can cooperate\Nwith the investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:03.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand you have personal\Ncircumstances to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.01,0:18:06.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially since you live in America...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:10.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to continue living\Nwith my fiancé in America,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:12.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he and I were to be\Nmarried this spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:14.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But now that he's dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.56,0:18:17.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what I'll do now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:18.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:21.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I've come this far,\NI'll push a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.61,0:18:24.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're still very young and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:27.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be involved\Nin such a dangerous investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:28.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.24,0:18:30.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anything to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:31.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:34.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all I want to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:36.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me investigate with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.09,0:18:46.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:50.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, may I see something that may act\Nas some form of personal ID?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:52.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:54.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:18:58.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, that name I gave you earlier\Nwas not my real name...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.69,0:19:00.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:01.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:04.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:07.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Who would have thought\Nyou were being so careful?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:09.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one step ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:13.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's even further proof\Nthat you're qualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.49,0:19:15.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is a Japanese driver's license okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:16.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:37.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:57.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but why do you always\Npay such close attention to your watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:20:00.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:02.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:07.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:39.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:42.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:44.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:49.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My father's cell phone is on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.30,0:20:51.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:55.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing I want to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:59.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good bye, Miss Naomi Misora.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:28.76,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I dreamed a dream that no one could see,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:34.14,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I threw away everything that I didn't need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:43.14,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm holding these feelings\Nthat I can't give up in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.27,0:21:49.53,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Even if my feet fall victim\Nto the shackles of sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.61,0:21:54.11,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}In between reality and my ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.91,0:21:59.83,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I can't hold back the flooding impulses
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.87,0:22:07.25,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Because I have a strong desire\Nto accomplish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:12.47,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}[deceit] [fear] [vanity] [melancholy]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.55,0:22:23.18,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm not weak enough to believe\Nany of these negative perceptions
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.68,0:22:29.02,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm a trickster who doesn't know solitude
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.33,0:22:42.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With Ryuk's information\Nand my prior preparations,
